Package ohos.media.common

Class VideoProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.media.common.VideoProperty

  • public final class VideoProperty
extends Object
    Describes video properties.
    • The getRecorderFps() method obtains the video frame capture rate.
    • The getRecorderDegrees() method obtains the video rotation angle.
    • The getRecorderRate() method obtains the video frame rate.
    • The getRecorderWidth() method obtains the video width.
    • The getRecorderHeight() method obtains the video height.
    • The getRecorderVideoEncoder() method obtains the video encoding format.
    • The getRecorderBitRate() method obtains the video encoding bit rate.
    Since:
    1
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Multimedia#MEDIA
